source_string: Once you've gathered the required crafting ingredients, tap the recipe once more, then move it from the output slot to your hotbar or inventory.
translation: 收集到所需的合成原料后，请再次点击配方，然后将其从输出槽移动到快捷栏或物品栏。

source_string: Redstone Dust comes from Redstone Ore. This dust transmits an electrical signal. When it has power it lights up and transmits its signal to other Redstone items that are next to it.
translation: 红石粉来自红石矿石。这种粉可传输电子信号。具有能量时，它将点亮并将其信号传输给邻近的其他红石物品。
context: How To Play help text. {MaxLength="500"}

source_string: In order for one of these items to be powered, it needs a power source such as a Lever, Button, or Pressure Plate. Experiment to find them all!
translation: 若要为其中一个物品提供能量，它需要诸如拉杆、按钮或压力板等能量源。试着找到全部能量源！

source_string: Place some Redstone Dust next to a power source and turn it on to power it.
translation: 在能量源旁边放置一些红石粉并开启它来赋予能量。

source_string: There are many items that use a Redstone signal to do something, such as a Hopper or a Piston.
translation: 有许多物品会使用红石信号来发挥作用，例如漏斗或活塞。

source_string: Redstone allows for endless possibilities! Try creating something useful for yourself like an automatic farm!
translation: 红石可以实现无限可能性！试着为自己创建一些有用的东西，例如自动农场！

source_string: A social hub for you and all the members of the Realm. Share your adventures and creations by posting stories to the Story Feed, like and comment to celebrate stories posted by other members.
translation: 您与所有 Realm 成员的社交中心。在故事动态中发布故事，分享您的冒险与创作。点赞并评论其他成员发布的故事，互相赞美和鼓励。

source_string: Clicking the ADD STORY button on the Story Feed will let you write a story of your own. You can choose to include a screenshot or text (or both!). Clicking the POST button will post your text/screenshot to the Story Feed for all the Realm's members to enjoy. If you don't have any screenshots to post, use the §ecamera§f:camera: on the game menu to capture the moment.
translation: 点击故事动态中的“添加故事”按钮，即可书写自己的故事。您可以选择包含屏幕截图或文本（或两者都包含！）。点击“发布”按钮会将文本/屏幕截图发布至故事动态，供所有 Realm 成员欣赏。若没有要发布的屏幕截图，请使用游戏菜单上的§e摄像机§f:camera:来捕捉这一时刻。

source_string: Whenever there is a new story in the Feed that you haven't read yet, a number will appear on the REALMS STORIES button. You'll always know when there is something new to read from your Realm's community. If you like what someone shared, go ahead and leave them a like or comment on their story!
translation: 每当动态中出现尚未阅读的新故事时，“Realms 故事”按钮上就会出现一个数字。您随时能了解自己所在 Realm 社区中是否有新的内容可供阅读。如果喜欢别人分享的内容，请积极点赞或评论他们的故事！

source_string: See who's playing and when in the Timeline. Scroll through the members of the Realm to see when they played last and who they played with. Use this information to set up times when you can all play together.
translation: 在时间线中查看谁在玩游戏及其何时游玩。滚动浏览 Realm 成员，了解他们上次游玩时间以及与谁一起玩。利用此信息安排大家能一起玩游戏的时间。

source_string: Know who is on the Realm
translation: 了解 Realm 中的其他成员

source_string: Get to know who is part of the Realm by using the Members tab. It's a list of all the players who can play here. You can see who the Realm owner is, who the operators are, and who has joined Realms Stories for this Realm. There are search, sort, and filter options to help you find exactly who you're looking for.
translation: 使用“成员”选项卡，了解 Realm 的成员。这个列表包含能在此玩游戏的所有玩家。您可以查看谁是 Realm 的所有者，谁是操作员，谁加入了此 Realm 的 Realms 故事。这里有搜索、排序和筛选选项，有助于准确查找所要寻找的人。

source_string: Realms Stories is available in the game menu when you're playing in the Realm and on the Realms Tab. You can keep up to date and tell your story from anywhere you are, even when you aren't playing. From your console, computer, and mobile device, Realms Stories is available everywhere.
translation: 当您在 Realm 中玩游戏时，可在游戏菜单和 Realms 选项卡上找到 Realms 故事。即使不在玩游戏，您也可以随时随地了解最新动态并讲述自己的故事。通过您的主机、电脑和移动设备，Realms 故事随处可用。

source_string: Scaffolding can help you create huge structures safely! You can walk inside scaffolding and stand on it. If you have a column of scaffolding you can go upward by standing in the scaffolding and pressing :_input_key.jump:. If you want to travel downward you can press :_input_key.sneak:.
translation: 脚手架可以帮助您安全地建造巨大的建筑！您可以在脚手架内部行走，也可以站在上面。如果您拥有一列脚手架，您可以通过站在脚手架内并按 :_input_key.jump: 来向上移动。如果您想向下移动，您可以按 :_input_key.sneak:。

source_string: Scaffolding can help you create huge structures safely! You can walk inside scaffolding and stand on it. If you have a column of scaffolding you can go upward by standing in the scaffolding and pressing :_input_key.jump:. If you want to travel downward you can press and hold :_input_key.sneak:.
translation: 脚手架可以帮助您安全地建造巨大的建筑！您可以在脚手架内部行走，也可以站在上面。如果您拥有一列脚手架，您可以通过站在脚手架内并按 :_input_key.jump: 来向上移动。如果您想向下移动，您可以按住 :_input_key.sneak:。

source_string: Scaffolding can help with building large structures by offering a way to reach higher places and safely descend without taking fall damage.
translation: 脚手架可让你能到达更高的地方，且在不受坠落伤害的情况下安全下降，以此来方便你建造大型结构。

source_string: When using the D-Pad control scheme, tap :touch_jump: to climb up a column of scaffolding. Tap :touch_fly_down: to climb down.
translation: 使用方向键控制方案时，点击 :touch_jump: 爬上一列脚手架。点击 :touch_fly_down: 向下爬。

source_string: When using a Joystick control scheme, press :tip_virtual_button_jump: to climb up a column of scaffolding. Tap :tip_virtual_button_sneak: to climb down.
translation: 使用摇杆控制方案时，点击 :tip_virtual_button_jump: 爬上一列脚手架。点击 :tip_virtual_button_sneak: 向下爬。

source_string: Scaffolding can help you create huge structures safely! You can walk inside scaffolding and stand on it. If you have a column of scaffolding you can go upward by standing in the scaffolding and pressing :rift_A:. If you want to travel downward you can press and hold :rift_X:.
translation: 脚手架可以帮助您安全地建造巨大的建筑！您可以在脚手架内部行走，也可以站在上面。如果您拥有一列脚手架，您可以通过站在脚手架内并按 :rift_A: 来向上移动。如果您想向下移动，您可以按住 :rift_X:。

source_string: Scaffolding can help you create huge structures safely! You can walk inside scaffolding and stand on it. If you have a column of scaffolding you can go upward by standing in the scaffolding and pressing :windowsmr_right_touchpad:. If you want to travel downward you can press and hold :windowsmr_right_stick:.
translation: 脚手架可以帮助您安全地建造巨大的建筑！您可以在脚手架内部行走，也可以站在上面。如果您拥有一列脚手架，您可以通过站在脚手架内并按 :windowsmr_right_touchpad: 来向上移动。如果您想向下移动，您可以按住 :windowsmr_right_stick:。

source_string: Scaffolding needs support. You can only place so many scaffolding horizontally without touching a different block. When you attempt to place too many scaffolding blocks without proper support, it will fall. Scaffolding can be placed like normal blocks, but it can also be placed on its own foundation to quickly build a tall tower.
translation: 脚手架需要支撑。您只能在水平方向放置若干个脚手架而不接触到不同的方块。当您试图在没有适当支撑的情况下放置过多的脚手架时，它会倒塌。脚手架可以像普通的方块一样进行放置，但它也可以被放置在自己的地基上，以便快速建成一座高塔。

source_string: When Scaffolding is broken it will also break every Scaffolding block that was being supported by it. This will let you quickly clean up your scaffolding by breaking the supporting blocks!
translation: 当脚手架被破坏时，它也会破坏由它所支撑的每一个脚手架。这将让您能够通过破坏支撑方块来快速清理您的脚手架！

source_string: Put on some fresh pixels and express yourself with a huge variety of inspired looks.
translation: 穿上一些新鲜的像素，用各种各样的灵感造型来展现自己。

source_string: Structure Blocks give creators the ability to copy and save out sections of their world into structures. Saved structures can then be pasted back into the world.
translation: 结构方块使得创建者们能够将世界的部分复制并保存为结构。所保存的结构在之后又可以粘贴回世界中。

source_string: To get a Structure Block you must use the /give slash command. To use a Structure Block, you must have Operator permissions.
translation: 要获得结构方块，您必须使用 /give 斜杠命令。要使用结构方块，您必须具有操作员权限。

source_string: Structure Blocks have 4 modes that can be switched between with the Mode dropdown: Save, Load, Corner, and 3D Export.
translation: 结构方块有 4 种模式：保存、加载、角落和 3D 导出，您可以使用模式下拉菜单在它们之间进行切换。

source_string: Save mode saves an area of the world as a structure. ##
translation: 保存模式会将世界的一个区域保存为一个结构。

source_string: Load mode loads a structure into the world. Only structures saved to the world or included in a behavior pack that is applied to the world can be loaded. ##
translation: 加载模式会将结构加载到世界中。只有保存至世界中的结构或者世界中应用的行为包所包含的结构才能被加载。

source_string: Corner mode is used with save mode's detect button to automatically set the area you want to save. See the Corner Mode section below for more details.  ##
translation: 角模式与保存模式的检测按钮一起使用，以自动设置要保存的区域。详细信息，请参阅下面的”角落模式“部分。

source_string: 3D Export exports a 3D model file on supported platforms.  ##
translation: 3D 导出会在支持的平台上导出 3D 模型文件。

source_string: On the right side of the Structure Block screen, a preview of the area you have selected or the structure to load will appear depending on the mode the block is in.
translation: 在结构方块屏幕的右侧，将根据方块所处的模式，显示您所选择的区域或者要加载的结构的预览。

source_string: Press :_input_key.attack: and drag, to rotate the 3D preview.
translation: 按 :_input_key.attack: 并拖动，以旋转 3D 预览。
使用 :_gamepad_stick_right: 以旋转 3D 预览。

source_string: Touch and drag on the preview to rotate the 3D preview.
translation: 触摸并拖动预览以旋转 3D 预览。

source_string: Redstone can be used to activate a Structure Block. This will cause it to either save a structure out or load a structure into the world, depending on the mode of the block and its settings.
translation: 红石可以用来激活一个结构方块。根据方块的模式及其设置，这会导致红石将结构保存到外部或将结构加载入世界。

source_string: You can change how much of a structure is loaded in by changing the values for Integrity and Seed.
translation: 您可以通过更改完整性和种子的值来更改某个结构的加载量。

source_string: Integrity - the percentage of blocks to load in from the structure, accepted values are 0 to 100. Blocks will be chosen randomly if a Seed is not specified. ##
translation: 完整性——从结构中加载的方块的百分比，接受的值是 0 到 100。如果没有指定种子，将随机选择方块。

source_string: Seed - the value entered here will determine which blocks to remove when using Integrity. Leave this field blank if you want the blocks to be chosen randomly. ##
translation: 种子——在这里输入的值将决定在使用完整性时将删除哪些方块。如果您希望随机选择方块，请将此字段留空。

source_string: When a structure with Structure Void blocks is loaded into the world, any block that would have been removed where the structure void block is loading into, will instead stay in the world.
translation: 当一个带有结构空位方块的结构被加载到世界中时，结构空位方块加载目的地上的任何原本可能被移除的方块将会转而留在该世界中。

source_string: Example: loading an empty shipwreck into the bottom of the ocean will normally copy air over the water blocks. If the shipwreck was filled with structure void, then the water will stay, and you will have a shipwreck filled with water.  ##
translation: 举例：在把一艘空的沉船加载到海底时，通常会在水方块上方复制空气。如果沉船充满了结构空位，那么水就会留下来，您就会获得一个充满水的沉船了。

source_string: To automatically select the area you want to save, you can place Corner Mode blocks around your structure and name them with the same name as the structure you want to save.  ##
translation: 要自动选择要保存的区域，您可以在结构周围放置角落模式方块，并使用与要保存的结构相同的名称来命名它们。

source_string: Pressing the Detect button in Save mode will find all of the Corner Blocks with the same name and create a selection area so that it will save everything inside of the volume those Corner Blocks make. ##
translation: 在保存模式下按下检测按钮将找到所有具有相同名称的角落方块，并创建一个选择区域，以便保存这些角落方块所生成的卷中的所有内容。

source_string: Combine two Shulker Shells with a Chest to create a Shulker Box. Shulker Shells are dropped by Shulkers found in End Cities. Unlike other containers, Shulker Boxes keep their items when broken. Shulker Boxes will break and drop as an item if pushed by Pistons, and can be placed using Dispensers.
translation: 将两个潜影壳与箱子结合来制作潜影盒。潜影壳是末地城中的潜影贝掉落之物。与其他容器不同，潜影盒被损坏后会保留它们的物品。被活塞推动的潜影盒会损坏并且会作为物品掉落，可以使用发射器来放置潜影盒。

source_string: How to Play: The Crafting Table
Ready to take your crafting to the next level? Place four planks in a square in your crafting grid, and you'll get a §ecrafting table§f :crafting_table: - a whole new way to craft.
translation: 准备好让你的合成造诣更上一层楼了吗？将四块木板以正方形排列放入网格合成表，这样你就会得到一张§e工作台§f:crafting_table:，它将为你带来全新的合成方式。

source_string: Place your crafting table in the world, then right-click it to open it. The larger crafting grid will let you make bigger and better things, including tools, beds, and doors.
translation: 将你的工作台放置在世界中，然后右键点击打开。可合成的物品包括工具、床还有门等等，网格合成表越大，可合成的物品就会更大更好。

source_string: Place your crafting table in the world, then walk up to it and press :_input_key.use: to open it. The larger crafting grid will let you make bigger and better things, including tools, beds, and doors.
translation: 将你的工作台放置在世界中，然后走到工作台附近，按下 :_input_key.use: 打开。可合成的物品包括工具、床还有门等等，网格合成表越大，可合成的物品就会更大更好。

source_string: Place your crafting table in the world, then tap it to open it. The larger crafting grid will let you make bigger and better things, including tools, beds, and doors.
translation: 将你的工作台放置在世界中，然后点击打开。可合成的物品包括工具、床还有门等等，网格合成表越大，可合成的物品就会更大更好。

source_string: The End is another dimension which can be accessed through an active End Portal. The End Portal can be found in a Stronghold, which is deep underground in the Overworld.
translation: 末地是可通过激活的末地传送门进入的另外一个维度。末地传送门可在要塞之中找到，要塞位于主世界的地底深处。

source_string: Every End Portal Frame block is missing something mysterious to bring out the power within.
translation: 每个末地传送门框架方块都缺少一些神秘之物来诱发内部的能量。
context: How To Play help text. {MaxLength="500"}

source_string: Once the portal is active, jump into it to go to The End.
translation: 传送门被激活后，跳入其中即可前往末地。

source_string: The End is home to the dreaded Ender Dragon. She is a fierce and powerful enemy and seems to draw power from strange crystals. Her breath and fireball attacks leave lingering acid across the battlefield. Bring some friends to ensure your victory!
translation: 末地是可怕的末影龙的家园。她是既凶残又强大的敌人，似乎能从奇异水晶中汲取力量。她的龙息和火球攻击可以在整个战地留下滞留酸性物。带上一些好友以确保取得胜利！

source_string: If once wasn't enough, add four End Crystals to the exit portal corners to reawaken the Ender Dragon.
translation: 一次不行的话，可以将四颗末地水晶添加到返回传送门的各个角落来重新唤醒末影龙。
context: How To Play help text. {MaxLength="500"}

source_string: Texture packs visually transform the game's appearance, applying a fresh coat of paint to your Minecraft world.
translation: 材质包在视觉上改变了游戏的外观，让您的 Minecraft 世界焕然一新。

source_string: There are many tools in Minecraft that will allow you mine blocks faster than your fist. Tools can be crafted from Wood, Stone, Iron, Gold, Diamond, or Netherite.
translation: 在《我的世界》中有许多工具，用来开采方块比徒手开采要快得多。这些工具可使用木头、石头、铁、黄金、钻石或下界合金合成。

source_string: Using the right tool for the job will not only mine that block faster, but will also lose less durability. More complex tools must be created in order to mine rarer resources.
translation: 使用合适的工具进行工作不仅可以让您更快速地开采方块，而且还能够减慢耐久度消耗。若要开采更稀有的资源，必须制作更复杂的工具。

source_string: The Pickaxe is good at breaking hard blocks like Cobblestone, Iron, or Furnaces.
translation: 镐非常适合用来破坏坚硬的方块，例如圆石、铁或熔炉。

source_string: The Axe is good at breaking wooden blocks like Logs, Planks, or Crafting Tables.
translation: 斧头非常适合用来破坏木质方块，例如原木、木板或工作台。

source_string: The Shovel is good at breaking loose blocks like Dirt, Sand, and Gravel. Shovels can also create a path by pressing :_input_key.use: on grass blocks.
translation: 锹非常适合用来破坏疏松的方块，例如泥土、沙子和砂砾。锹还可用于创建草径，只要在草方块上按 :_input_key.use: 即可。

source_string: The Shovel is good at breaking loose blocks like Dirt, Sand, and Gravel. Shovels can also create a path by tapping on grass blocks.
translation: 锹非常适合用来破坏疏松的方块，例如泥土、沙子和砂砾。锹还可用于创建草径，只要在草方块上进行点击即可。

source_string: The Hoe is required for tilling Dirt to plant crops. Press :_input_key.use: on Dirt or Grass blocks to turn them into Farmland.
translation: 需要使用锄头来耕作泥土从而种植农作物。在泥土或草方块上按 :_input_key.use: 可让它们转换为农地。

source_string: The Hoe is required for tilling Dirt to plant crops. Tap Dirt or Grass blocks to turn them into Farmland.
translation: 需要使用锄头来耕作泥土从而种植农作物。点击泥土或草方块可让它们转换为农地。

source_string: All of these tools can accept enchantments, either from the Enchanting Table or Anvil.
translation: 所有这些工具都可接受附魔，无论是从附魔台还是铁砧进行附魔。

source_string: There are even more tools to aid you on your adventure:
translation: 还有更多工具可协助您冒险：

source_string: A Bucket will allow you to collect things like Water, Milk, Lava, and even Fish.
translation: 使用桶可以收集水、奶、熔岩，甚至鱼等物体。

source_string: Flint & Steel allows you to light fires... be careful in densely wooded areas!
translation: 使用打火石可以点火...在树林茂密的区域使用时需小心！

source_string: A Fishing Rod lets you catch fish and other loot from water blocks. It can also be used to pull other players and mobs. Fishing Rods can also be enchanted!
translation: 使用钓鱼竿可以从水方块中捕获鱼和其他战利品。还可使用它拖动其他玩家和生物。钓鱼竿也可以附魔！

source_string: Shears are very handy for collecting items like Wool, Leaves, and Cobwebs.
translation: 剪刀非常适合收集羊毛、树叶和蜘蛛网等物品。

source_string: Trading can be done in villages. Each villager has a profession; they can be Farmers, Butchers, Blacksmiths, Cartographers, Librarians, or Priests. Some professions will trade for items that other professions cannot. Explore and trade with many villagers to find all the trades.
translation: 在村庄中可进行交易。每个村民都有一项职业，他们可能是农民、屠夫、铁匠、制图师、图书管理员或牧师。有些职业可以交易其他职业无法交易的物品。探索并与许多村民交易以找到所有的可进行交易。
用于换取绿宝石的商品

source_string: You can find out what a villager is offering as trade by interacting with them. A villager may adjust the price of a trade whenever a player trades with it. A villager may run out of stock, temporarily disabling the trade if it is used too frequently. Trades usually involve buying or selling items for emeralds.
translation: 您可以通过与村民互动来了解他们会提供什么来进行交易。村民可能会在与玩家交易时调整交易价格。村民可能会缺货，或者由于过于频繁地使用某项交易从而导致其暂时被禁用。交易通常涉及到绿宝石的买卖。

source_string: As you trade with villagers, they will get better at their profession and start to offer better and more valuable trades.
translation: 当您与村民进行交易时，他们的职业水平会提高，并开始提供更好、更有价值的交易。

source_string: Take care of your villagers, they need to rest, work, and eat to thrive.
translation: 照顾好您的村民，他们需要休息、工作和吃饭才能茁壮成长。

source_string: There are many ways to get around other than walking or riding a mount or flying.
translation: 除了步行、骑乘或飞行外，还有很多方法可以到达各地。

source_string: Minecarts are ridable carts that roll on Rails. You can make the Rails go wherever you want by placing them next to each other. Place a Minecart on the Rails and you are ready to ride.
translation: 矿车是在轨道上运行的小车，可以乘坐。通过连接放置，你可以造出通往任意地点的轨道。将矿车放置在轨道上，你就可以乘坐了。

source_string: Minecarts are ridable carts that roll on Rails, which you can build to go anywhere. Just place multiple Rails next to each other, place a Minecart on it, and you're ready to ride.
translation: 矿车是在轨道上运行的小车，可以乘坐，建造后可用于前往任何地方。只需将多个轨道并排放置，将矿车放置在铁轨上，您就可以乘坐了。

source_string: Press :_input_key.use: while looking at a Minecart to hop in and ride. Press :_input_key.forward: to roll forward. Press :_input_key.jump: or :_input_key.sneak: to get out.
translation: 在看着矿车时按 :_input_key.use: 跃上并乘坐。按 :_input_key.forward: 向前滚动。按 :_input_key.jump: 或 :_input_key.sneak: 跃下。

source_string: Press :_input_key.use: while looking at a Minecart to hop in and ride. Push :_gamepad_stick_left: forward to roll forward. Press :_input_key.jump: or :_input_key.sneak: to get out.
translation: 在看到矿车时按 :_input_key.use: 跃上并乘坐。向前推 :_gamepad_stick_left: 可向前滚动。按 :_input_key.jump: 或 :_input_key.sneak: 可跃下。

source_string: Look at a Minecart and tap "Ride" to hop in.
translation: 看向一辆矿车，然后点击“骑乘”即可跳进去。

source_string: When using the D-Pad control scheme, tap and hold :touch_forward: to start moving forward and build momentum, and tap :touch_jump: to get out.
translation: 使用方向键控制方案时，长按 :touch_forward: 开始前进并加速，点击 :touch_jump: 即可离开。

source_string: When using a Joystick control scheme, drag :tip_virtual_joystick: up to start moving forward and build momentum, and tap :tip_virtual_button_dismount: to get out.
translation: 使用摇杆控制方案时，向上拖动 :tip_virtual_joystick: 开始前进并加速，点击  :tip_virtual_button_dismount: 即可离开。

source_string: Boats let you travel across water. Place one on a water block and you are ready to go.
translation: 船让您可以在水面上旅行，将一艘船放置在水方块上即可出发。

source_string: Boats let you travel across water. Just place one on a water block and you're ready to go.
translation: 船让您可以在水面上旅行，只需将一艘船放置在水方块上即可出发。

source_string: Press :_input_key.use: while looking at a Boat to board it. Press :_input_key.left: or :_input_key.right: to turn left or right. Press :_input_key.forward: to move forward. Press :_input_key.jump: or :_input_key.sneak: to get out.
translation: 在看到船时按 :_input_key.use: 可上船。按 :_input_key.left: 或 :_input_key.right: 可向左或向右转。按 :_input_key.forward: 可向前移动。按 :_input_key.jump: 或 :_input_key.sneak: 可下船。

source_string: Press :_input_key.use: while looking at a Boat to board it. Push :_gamepad_stick_left: left or right to turn. Push :_gamepad_stick_left: forward to move forward. Press :_input_key.jump: or :_input_key.sneak: to get out.
translation: 在看到船时按 :_input_key.use: 可上船。按 :_gamepad_stick_left: 左键或右键可调整方向。按 :_gamepad_stick_left: 前键可向前移动。按 :_input_key.jump: 或 :_input_key.sneak: 可下船。

source_string: Look at a Boat and tap "Board" to board it.
translation: 看向一艘船，然后点击“上船”即可登上船只。

source_string: When using the D-Pad control scheme, tap :touch_left: or :touch_right: to turn left or right, or tap and hold both to move forward. Tap "Leave Boat" to get out.
translation: 使用方向键控制方案时，点击 :touch_left: 或 :touch_right: 向左或向右转动，或同时长按两者以向前移动。点击“离开船”即可下船。

source_string: When using a Joystick control scheme, drag :tip_virtual_joystick: up to move forward and tap :tip_virtual_button_dismount: to get out.
translation: 使用摇杆控制方案时，向上拖动 :tip_virtual_joystick: 向前移动，点击 :tip_virtual_button_dismount: 即可离开。

source_string: The Sword is the primary melee weapon in Minecraft. It can be made from Wood, Stone, Iron, Gold, Diamond, or Netherite. Jump attacks do critical damage!
translation: 剑是《我的世界》中的主要近战武器。可以使用木头、石头、铁、黄金、钻石或下界合金制成。跳劈会造成暴击伤害！

source_string: Press :_input_key.attack: with a Sword in your hand to attack.
translation: 在手持剑时按 :_input_key.attack: 即可进行攻击。
点击生物对其进行攻击。

source_string: The Bow is the primary ranged weapon in Minecraft. Press and hold :_input_key.use: to draw the bow back. Release :_input_key.use: to fire an arrow. The bow requires arrows to fire.
translation: 弓是《我的世界》中的主要远程武器。按住 :_input_key.use: 可拉弓。释放 :_input_key.use: 可射箭。弓在有箭的情况下才能射出。

source_string: The Bow is the primary ranged weapon in Minecraft. Press and hold the Screen to draw the bow back. Release the press to fire an arrow. The bow requires arrows to fire.
translation: 弓是《我的世界》中的主要远程武器。按住屏幕可拉弓。释放所按屏幕可射箭。弓在有箭的情况下才能射出。

source_string: Bows do more damage the further they are pulled back, make sure to pull it all the way back.
translation: 弦往后拉得越多，弓造成的伤害就越大，请确保将弦拉满。

source_string: The Crossbow is an alternate ranged weapon. Press and hold :_input_key.use: to load the crossbow. Once the Crossbow is loaded, it will stay loaded until it is fired. Press :_input_key.use: to fire an arrow. The Crossbow requires arrows to load.
translation: 弩是一种备用远程武器。按住 :_input_key.use: 可装填弩。弩装填成功后，将会一直保持装填状态，直到你将箭射出。按下 :_input_key.use: 可射出一枚箭。装填弩需要箭。

source_string: The crossbow is a ranged weapon which requires an arrow to be loaded. Tap and hold anywhere on the screen to load the crossbow with an arrow.
translation: 弩是一种远程武器，需要装入箭矢。长按屏幕上的任意位置，为弩装填箭矢。

source_string: Once you've loaded the crossbow it'll stay loaded until fired, even when you put it in your inventory.
translation: 弩装填完毕后，即使你把它放在物品栏中，它也会保持装填状态，可随时射击。

source_string: Tap anywhere on the screen to fire a loaded crossbow.
translation: 点击屏幕上的任意位置即可用装填好的弩射击。

source_string: If you're using Action Buttons, tap :tip_virtual_button_action_build_or_use: to fire a loaded crossbow.
translation: 如果您使用的是动作按钮，点击 :tip_virtual_button_action_build_or_use: 用装填好的弩射击。

source_string: The Trident is a dual-purpose melee and ranged weapon. Press :_input_key.attack: to attack. Press and hold :_input_key.use: to draw the trident back. Release :_input_key.use: to throw the trident. The Trident is the best weapon underwater.
translation: 三叉戟是近战和远程两用武器。按 :_input_key.attack: 可攻击。按住 :_input_key.use: 可将三叉戟收回。释放 :_input_key.use: 可投掷三叉戟。三叉戟是最好的水下武器。

source_string: The Trident is a dual-purpose melee and ranged weapon. Tap mobs to attack them. Press and hold the Screen to draw the trident back. Release the press to throw the trident. The Trident is the best weapon underwater.
translation: 三叉戟是近战和远程两用武器。点击生物可攻击它们。按住屏幕可将三叉戟收回。释放所按屏幕可投掷三叉戟。三叉戟是最好的水下武器。

source_string: The Sword, Bow, Crossbow, and Trident have specific enchantments that you can get from the Enchanting Table or Anvil that will improve damage, durability and even light mobs on fire!
translation: 您可从附魔台或铁砧为剑、弓、弩和三叉戟获取特定附魔，它们将提高伤害值、耐久度甚至可以放火烧生物！

source_string: Worlds in the Minecraft Marketplace Minecraft levels where our partners have altered the terrain and placed new blocks to create amazing structures and terrain for you to explore and enjoy.
translation: Minecraft 市场 Minecraft 等级中的世界，其中我们的合作伙伴改变了地形并放置了新的方块，以创建令人惊叹的结构和地形供您探索和享受。

source_string: Worlds can also include new items, mobs, blocks and even custom gameplay.
translation: 世界也可以包括新的物品、生物、方块，甚至是自定义游戏玩法。

source_string: All of the content in the Marketplace is created by our professional commiunity creators.
translation: 市场中的所有内容均由我们的专业社区创作者所创建。

source_string: Worlds can do so much, we've created several Sub-Categories to help describe what they can do:
translation: 世界可以有很多功能，我们创建了几个子类别来帮助描述相关的功能：

source_string: Mini-Games are smaller worlds that include new game mechanics, challenges, or rules.
translation: 小游戏是较小的世界，包括新的游戏机制、挑战或规则。

source_string: These games are made with multiplayer in mind, letting you test your skills and have fun with your friends.
translation: 这些游戏在制作时考虑到多人游戏，允许测试自己的技能并与朋友一起玩乐。

source_string: Survival Spawns let you start playing in a custom-built world, while still enjoying the classic survival mechanics of Minecraft.
translation: 生存生成允许在自定义的世界中开始游戏，同时仍然享受 Minecraft 的经典生存机制。

source_string: Just like in Survival mode you will have health and hunger, and need to fight dangerous mobs.
translation: 就像生存模式一样，您会拥有生命值和饥饿度，并且需要与危险的生物战斗。

source_string: Adventure Maps let you use Minecraft to play a totally different kind of game.
translation: 冒险地图允许使用 Minecraft 玩一种迥然不同的游戏。

source_string: You can not break blocks or place new blocks in these worlds.
translation: 您不能在这些世界中打破方块或放置新方块。

source_string: Dynamic Worlds allow you to explore the creative designs of our marketplace creators in a randomly generated map.
translation: 动态世界允许在随机生成的地图中探索我们市场创作者的创意设计。

source_string: Worlds can have new biomes, customized structures (randomly generated buildings), new blocks, textures, and mobs.
translation: 世界可以拥有新的生物群系、自定义结构（随机生成的建筑）、新的方块、材质和生物。

source_string: How to Play: Your First Craft
Many blocks, like wood, can be turned into useful items by crafting. To do this, you'll find a simple §ecrafting grid§f on the right-hand side of your inventory screen.
translation: 木头等很多方块都可以通过合成变为有用的物品。如果想要进行合成，你需要在物品栏界面的右侧找到一个简单的§e网格合成表§f。

source_string: For example, put a single wood log anywhere on the crafting grid, and several planks will appear in the §eoutput slot§f.
translation: 例如，只要在网格合成表的任意位置放一个原木，那么§e输出槽§f中就会出现几块木板。

source_string: Simply tap your shiny new planks and they will appear in your hotbar. Now you're ready to place them into the world!
translation: 只需点击这些崭新的木板，它们就会出现在快捷栏中。这样就可以把它们放置在世界中了！

source_string: Simply drag your shiny new planks to your hotbar. Now you're ready to place them into the world!
translation: 只需将这些崭新的木板拖动到快捷栏，就可以把它们放置在世界中了！

source_string: Simply select your shiny new planks and they will appear in your hotbar. Now you're ready to place them into the world!
translation: 只需选择这些崭新的木板，它们就会出现在快捷栏中。这样就可以把它们放置在世界中了！

source_string: Some items require you to place your crafting ingredients in a certain shape - also called a §erecipe§f.
translation: 合成某些物品时，需要将合成原料摆放成特定的形状 - 也称为§e配方§f。

source_string: Try placing two planks above each other to create some sticks. Useful for all sorts of things!
translation: 试试将两块木板叠放在一起合成一些木棍。它们的用处可就大了！

source_string: This device is no longer supported.

Our ability to support this device is coming to an end. You will continue to receive updates until March of 2025, when you will receive your final update for this device.%sAfter you receive the final update, you will still be able to play on your worlds, and access Marketplace purchases (including Minecoins). Realms managed with this device will continue to work for 6 months unless they are updated by the Realm owner on a different device.%sTo cancel your Realm subscription, you will need to do so in the Settings menu for Subscriptions on the device the Realm was created with.%sYou will no longer receive the latest updates and will be unable to play multiplayer with devices or Realms which are continuing to receive updates. You will also not be able to connect to certain servers.%sClick on the button for more information.
translation: 我们即将无法支持此设备。目前您仍能继续收到更新，但到 2025 年 3 月为止，您将收到适用于此设备的最后一次更新。%s收到最终更新后，您仍然可以在您的世界中进行游戏，并访问市场购买内容（包括 Minecoins）。由此设备管理的 Realm 将继续运行 6 个月，除非 Realm 所有者选择在另一台设备上进行更新。%s要取消您的 Realm 订阅服务，您将需要在创建 Realm 的设备上，找到订阅服务的“设置”菜单进行此操作。%s您将不再收到最新的更新内容，且将无法与继续接收更新的设备或 Realm 进行多人游戏。您也将无法连接到某些服务器。%s单击按钮了解更多信息。

source_string: Our ability to support this device has come to an end. You will no longer receive updates as of March of 2025, and this is your final update for this device.%sYou will still be able to play on your worlds, and access Marketplace purchases (including Minecoins). Realms managed with this device will continue to work for 6 months from March of 2025 unless they are updated by the Realm owner on a different device.%sTo cancel your Realm subscription, you will need to do so in the Settings menu for Subscriptions on the device the Realm was created with.%sYou will no longer receive the latest updates and will be unable to play multiplayer with devices or Realms which are continuing to receive updates. You will also not be able to connect to certain servers.%sClick on the button for more information.
translation: 我们已无法支持此设备。从 2025 年 3 月开始，您将不再收到更新，这是此设备的最后一次更新。%s您仍然可以在您的世界中进行游戏，并访问市场购买内容（包括 Minecoins）。由此设备管理的 Realm 将自 2025 年 3 月起继续运行 6 个月，除非 Realm 所有者选择在另一台设备上进行更新。%s要取消您的 Realm 订阅服务，您将需要在创建 Realm 的设备上，找到订阅服务的“设置”菜单进行此操作。%s您将不再收到最新的更新内容，且将无法与继续接收更新的设备或 Realm 进行多人游戏。您也将无法连接到某些服务器。%s单击按钮了解更多信息。

source_string: Our ability to support this VR/MR graphic device has come to an end. This device will no longer be supported in updates after March of 2025, when you will receive your final update supporting this device.%sAfter you receive the final update, you will still receive updates on your PC and be able to play without a VR/MR device. From this point on you can keep building in your worlds, and your Marketplace purchases (including Minecoins) will continue to be available on a non-VR/MR graphics devices such as a computer monitor. You will no longer be able to use your VR/MR device with Minecraft as it will no longer be supported in the latest updates.%sClick on the button for more information.
translation: 我们已无法支持此 VR/MR 图形设备。2025 年 3 月之后的更新将不再支持此设备，届时您将收到支持此设备的最后一次更新。%s收到最终更新后，您仍然可以在 PC 上收到更新，也可以在没有 VR/MR 设备的情况下进行游戏。从现在开始，您可以继续在世界中进行创造，也可以在非 VR/MR 图形设备（如电脑显示器）上继续使用在市场购买的物品（包括 Minecoins）。您将无法在 Minecraft 中使用您的 VR/MR 设备，因为最新更新将不再支持此设备。%s单击按钮了解更多信息。

source_string: Our ability to support this VR/MR graphic device has come to an end. This VR/MR device is no longer supported. You have received the final update supporting this graphics device, and you will still receive updates on your PC and be able to play without a VR/MR device. From this point on you can keep building in your worlds, and your Marketplace purchases (including Minecoins) will continue to be available on a non-VR/MR graphics devices such as a computer monitor. You will no longer be able to use your VR/MR device with Minecraft as it will no longer be supported in the latest updates.%sClick on the button for more information. We know this is an inconvenience, and deeply appreciate the time you spent with our game, and your support.
translation: 我们已无法支持此 VR/MR 图形设备。此 VR/MR 设备不再受到支持。您已收到支持此图形设备的最后一次更新，您仍然可以在 PC 上收到更新，也可以在没有 VR/MR 设备的情况下进行游戏。从现在开始，您可以继续在世界中进行创造，也可以在非 VR/MR 图形设备（如电脑显示器）上继续使用在市场购买的物品（包括 Minecoins）。您将无法在 Minecraft 中使用您的 VR/MR 设备，因为最新更新将不再支持此设备。%s单击按钮了解更多信息。给您带来不便，我们深表歉意。同时我们也衷心感谢您为这款游戏付出的时间以及您的支持。

source_string: Resource packs are applied bottom to top. This means any asset that is in two packs will be overridden by the higher pack. Packs in your worlds will apply on top of these global packs. These resources are just for you. No one else will see the resources you set here. Resource Packs in your worlds or worlds you join will apply on top of these global resources.
translation: 资源包从下到上应用。这表示两个包中的任何资产都会由更高级的资源包覆盖。您世界中的这些资源包会应用于这些全局包上方。这些资源仅供您使用，别人无法看到您设置的资源。在您的世界中或您加入的世界中，资源包将应用于这些全局资源上方。

source_string: Behavior Packs are applied bottom to top. That means anything that is in two Behavior Packs will be overridden by the higher one.
translation: 行为包从下到上应用。这表示两种行为包中的任何内容都会由更高级的附加件覆盖。

translation: 添加钻石盔甲、武器或工具

source_string: Want to get the most out of your equipment? You'll need a Smithing Table.
translation: 想要充分利用设备？你需要一张锻造台。

source_string: Use it to make all kinds of changes, for example by upgrading Diamond equipment to Netherite, or by making cosmetic changes with Armor Trims.
translation: 使用它可以进行各种更改，例如，将钻石装备升级到下界合金，或使用纹饰盔甲进行外观更改。

source_string: In order to upgrade your equipment, you'll need a Smithing Template. You can find a large variety throughout the world, which can be used for all kinds of upgrades.
translation: 为了升级装备，你需要一个锻造模板。你可以在世界各地找到各种各样的模板，用于各种升级。

source_string: Place a Template into the leftmost slot of a Smithing Table to see which items you need for the upgrade.
translation: 将模板放入锻造台最左侧的槽中，看看升级需要哪些物品。

source_string: For example, to upgrade Diamond equipment to Netherite, you need a Netherite Upgrade Smithing Template, which you can find in Bastion Remnants. Then, place the Diamond equipment in the equipment slot and a Netherite ingot in the ingredient slot, and you're done!
translation: 例如，要将钻石装备升级到下界合金，你需要一个下界合金升级锻造模板，你可以在堡垒遗迹中找到锻造模板。然后，将钻石装备放入装备槽中，将下界合金锭放入配料槽，大功告成！

source_string: Item properties such as enchantments and armor trims will be retained, but the Smithing Template will be consumed when you upgrade your equipment. Don't worry - you can craft copies of them with your Crafting Table.
translation: 附魔物品和纹饰盔甲等物品属性将被保留，但锻造模板将在你升级装备时被消耗。别担心，你可以用你的工作台制作模板副本。

source_string: Get creative and customize the look of your armor with Armor Trims. You'll need an Armor Trim Smithing Template to get started, which you can find throughout the world.
translation: 发挥创意，使用纹饰盔甲来定制盔甲的外观。你需要一个盔甲装饰锻造模板才能开始，这种模板可以在世界各地找到。

source_string: Place a Template into the leftmost slot of a Smithing Table to see which items you need for the upgrade. Then place a piece of armor in the equipment slot and a crystal or ingot in the ingredient slot. Done!
translation: 将模板放入锻造台最左侧的槽中，看看升级需要哪些物品。然后在装备槽中放入一件盔甲，在配料槽中放入一块水晶或锭。完成了！

source_string: Only certain crystals and ingots can be used for Armor Trims. Try different kinds like Iron, Gold, or Lapis to create unique designs!
translation: 只有特定的水晶和金属锭可用于纹饰盔甲。请尝试用不同种类的铁、金或青金石来创造独特的设计！

source_string: Access to Marketplace Pass requires an active subscription, and a compatible version of Minecraft: Bedrock Edition with Minecraft Marketplace. Requires Microsoft account sign-in.
translation: 访问 Marketplace Pass 需要有活跃的订阅服务，以及带有 Minecraft 市场的《Minecraft：基岩版》兼容版本。需要登录 Microsoft 账号。
context: {StrContains="Marketplace Pass"}

source_string: What happens to my content after it leaves Marketplace Pass?
translation: 取消 Marketplace Pass 后，我的内容会发生什么？
context: {StrContains="Marketplace Pass"}

source_string: Once a world, texture pack, skin pack, or mash-up leaves the catalog, you will need to purchase the item from the Marketplace to continue playing. Packs will not be deleted from your local storage until you delete them. Monthly character creator items you’ve redeemed are yours to keep.
translation: 一旦世界、材质包、皮肤包或混搭包移出目录，您将需要从市场中购买物品来继续游玩。除非您手动删除包，否则包不会从您的本地存储中删除。所兑换的每月角色创建器物品均可保留。

source_string: What happens when my subscription ends?
translation: 订阅结束后会发生什么？

source_string: You will be able to purchase and download any world templates saved to your cloud storage within 18 months of ending your subscription unless they are no longer offered by Minecraft. Monthly character creator items you’ve redeemed are yours to keep.
translation: 在订阅结束后的 18 个月内，您将能够购买和下载任何保存到您的云存储中的世界模板，Minecraft 不再提供这些世界模板的情况除外。所兑换的每月角色创建器物品均可保留。

source_string: What's the difference between this and Realms Plus?
translation: 这和 Realms Plus 有什么不同？

source_string: The difference between the two subscriptions is that Realms Plus includes a personal server where you can play with up to ten friends at a time. The content catalog you have access to with your Marketplace Pass subscription is the same catalog that is available with a Realms Plus subscription.
translation: 两项订阅内容的区别在于，Realms Plus 的订阅内容包括个人服务器，服务器可支持同时与最多十位好友一起玩。订阅 Marketplace Pass 后可访问的内容目录与 Realms Plus 订阅的内容目录相同。
context: {StrContains="Marketplace Pass"}

source_string: Can I subscribe to both Marketplace Pass and Realms Plus?
translation: 我可以同时订阅 Marketplace Pass 与 Realms Plus 吗？
context: {StrContains="Marketplace Pass"}

source_string: A Realms Plus subscription includes Marketplace Pass. If you are subscribed to Marketplace Pass and want to explore Realms Plus, we suggest that you unsubscribe from Marketplace Pass first. Active Realms Plus subscribers are unable to subscribe to Marketplace Pass.
translation: Realms Plus 的订阅内容已包含 Marketplace Pass。如果在已订阅 Marketplace Pass 的情况下希望探索 Realms Plus，我们建议先取消订阅 Marketplace Pass。在已订阅 Realms Plus 的情况下，无法再订阅 Marketplace Pass。
context: {StrContains="Marketplace Pass"}

source_string: Can I use my Marketplace Pass content on any device?
translation: 我可以在任何设备上使用 Marketplace Pass 内容吗？
context: {StrContains="Marketplace Pass"}

source_string: If you purchase Marketplace Pass, you can access all the packs from any device with a  compatible version of Minecraft: Bedrock Edition with Minecraft Marketplace (sold separately) if you’re signed into your Minecraft account. Not supported on Amazon Kindle Fire or Minecraft Java Edition.
translation: 如果您购买了 Marketplace Pass，那么只要您使用的是带有 Minecraft Marketplace（单独出售）的《Minecraft：基岩版》兼容版本，且登录了您的 Minecraft 账号，就可以在任何设备上访问所有包。在 Amazon Kindle Fire 和 Minecraft Java 版上不受支持。
context: {StrContains="Marketplace Pass"}

translation: Twitch验证失败。请到mojang.com重新绑定您的Twitch账户。

translation: 无法连接到Twitch验证。请稍后再试。

translation: 无法载入集成的Twitch直播服务的库文件。

translation: 您的显卡至少需要支持OpenGL 3.0或通过扩展支持帧缓冲对象才能使用集成的Twitch直播功能。

translation: 很不幸，集成的Twitch直播功能需要更新的Mac OS X。你需要10.7 (Mac OS X Mountain Lion) 或更新的版本。您想访问apple.com来了解关于升级的信息吗？

Please click here to install it.

translation: 很不幸，由于未知原因，您现在无法在Twitch上同步直播 :'(

source_string: To play with friends please purchase the full game

source_string: In this trial you are limited to 90 minutes of play time. Craft, build, explore, and have fun! Your world will be preserved if you choose to purchase the full version.
translation: 在此试用版中，您只有90分钟的游戏时间去打造，建设，探索和享受您的世界！购买完整版以保留您的世界。

source_string: Explore, craft, build, and have fun! In this trial you will have 90 minutes of play time. Unlock the full game to continue playing as long as you want!
translation: 探索、合成、建造并享受乐趣！在此试用版中，您会拥有 90 分钟的探索时间。解锁完整版继续探索，多久都可以！

source_string: Explore, craft, build, and have fun! In this trial you will have 90 minutes of play time. Unlock the full game to play an infinite amount of worlds for as long as you want!*
translation: 探索、合成、建造并享受乐趣！在此试玩版中，您会拥有 90 分钟的游戏时间。解锁完整版游戏，探索无限世界，想玩多久都可以！*

translation: 探索、制作、建造并享受乐趣！在此试用版的世界中，您会拥有 90 分钟的游戏时间。发现错误？访问 bugs.mojang.com 进行报告！其他问题？查看我们的常见问题解答。

translation: 您有任何反馈要告诉我们吗？

source_string: Time has expired. Please purchase to unlock the full game:
translation: 时间已过期。请购买以解锁完整游戏：

source_string: Do you want to continue exploring, crafting, and building? Unlock the full game to play as long as you want! This world will be saved for you to pick up where you left off but you can't modify it until you unlock the full game.
translation: 您想继续探索、合成和建造吗？解锁完整版本，探索多久都可以！这个世界会为您保存好，供以后继续探索，但在解锁完整版本之前，您将无法修改。

source_string: Do you want to continue exploring, crafting, and building? Unlock the full game to play an infinite amount of worlds for as long as you want!*
translation: 您是否想继续探索、合成和建造？解锁完整版游戏，探索无限世界，想玩多久都可以！*

source_string: Do you want to continue exploring, crafting, and building? Start a new trial world to continue playing!
translation: 您想继续探索、制作和建造吗？开启试用版中的新世界继续玩游戏！
解锁《我的世界》完整游戏

source_string: Endlessly explore your own unique worlds and construct anything you can imagine - from the simplest of homes to the grandest of castles! Play Creative mode to build wonders with unlimited resources. Or mine in Survival mode, crafting weapons and armor to fend off dangerous mobs and survive the nights. Plus, play with friends online! Unlock the full game today!
translation: 无限探索您自己的独特世界，建造您能想象到的一切——从最简单的住宅，到最宏伟的城堡！您可以在创造模式中利用无限资源建造奇迹，也可以在生存模式中进行挖掘，合成武器和盔甲，抵御各种危险生物并在夜晚幸存下来。另外还可以在线与好友一起畅玩！立即解锁完整游戏！

source_string: With the full Minecraft experience you get Creative mode, achievements, and more, plus with a Microsoft account you can meet others in the Minecraft community! Join your friends' worlds, make new friends on Servers, and sync your Marketplace purchases to everywhere you play Minecraft.
translation: 您可以借助完整的 Minecraft 体验获得创造模式、成就等等，另外您还可以借助 Microsoft 账号在 Minecraft 社区中结识其他玩家！加入好友的世界，在服务器上结识新的好友，并将您的商店购买内容同步到您玩 Minecraft 的任何地方。

source_string: In addition to the full Minecraft experience with Creative mode, Multiplayer, and more, you'll earn achievements and a Gamerscore to mark your Minecraft progress and show your Microsoft account friends your accomplishments. Get the full game to start earning them!
translation: 除了获得带有创造模式、多人游戏等等的完整 Minecraft 体验，您还将获得成就和玩家分数。它们将记录您的 Minecraft 进度，并向您的 Microsoft 账号好友展示您的成就。立即获得完整游戏来开始获得它们！

source_string: The full Minecraft experience lets you enjoy Creative mode, achievements and Multiplayer with your friends across Minecraft devices! Play with friends on console, PC and mobile to create, explore and survive together. Unlock the full Minecraft experience today!
translation: 完整的 Minecraft 游戏体验能够让您享受创造模式、成就以及与您的好友在多种 Minecraft 设备上进行多人游戏！与控制台、电脑和移动端上的好友一起创造、探索和生存。立即解锁完整的 Minecraft 体验！

source_string: Servers offer some of the most creative ways to enjoy Minecraft! Play great mini-games, meet the Minecraft community and make new friends. Unlock the full Minecraft experience to try Servers today!
translation: 服务器提供了一些享受《我的世界》的最有创意的方式！玩精彩的小游戏，邂逅《我的世界》社区并结识新的好友。立即解锁完整的《我的世界》游戏体验以尝试服务器！

source_string: Get access to Minecraft Marketplace, our in-game store. Switch up your look with new skins, change your world, or explore incredible new maps from the best community creators! Get the full game today!
translation: 访问我们的游戏内商店——《我的世界》市场。用新的皮肤让自己焕然一新，更改您的世界，或者探索来自最佳的社区创建者的超赞新地图！立即获取完整游戏！

source_string: Buy Minecraft and get Creative mode! Access the entire inventory - the only limit to what you can build is your imagination! Fly around your world, make your dream home out of anything and everything, or just blow up a mountain with unlimited TNT!
translation: 购买《我的世界》并获得创造模式！访问整个物品栏——您能建造什么只取决于您的想象力！飞遍您的世界，用任何东西、一切东西建造您的梦想之家，或者干脆用无限量的 TNT 炸掉一座山！

source_string: Want to make wolves act like bunnies? Turn all the trees into cotton candy? You can alter everything in the full Minecraft experience with add-ons! Plus get access to Multiplayer, Creative mode, achievements and more! Buy Minecraft now for full access!
translation: 想让狼表现得像兔子一样吗？把所有的树都变成棉花糖？您可以在完整的 Minecraft 游戏体验中使用附加件改变一切！此外，您还可以访问多人游戏、创造模式、成就等等！立即购买 Minecraft 获得完整访问权限！

source_string: Unlock the full Minecraft experience and get access to Seeds! Seeds help you discover new biomes - survive on ice plains, ascend extreme hills, or trek across deserts. Start with unique templates or explore random new worlds! Access Seeds, Creative mode, Multiplayer and more by buying Minecraft today!
translation: 解锁完整的《我的世界》游戏体验，获得访问种子的权限！种子会帮助您发现新的生物群系——在冰原上生存，攀登险峻的峭壁，或者徒步穿越沙漠。立即以独特的模板开始游戏或探索随机的新世界！立即购买《我的世界》，获得访问种子、创造模式、多人游戏以及更多内容的权限！

source_string: Thank you for downloading the Minecraft Trial for Chromebook! Your playtesting will provide invaluable data for bug fixes and technical troubleshooting. Uncover a bug? Report it at bugs.mojang.com! Other questions? Check out our FAQ.
translation: 感謝您下载《我的世界》Chromebook 试用版！您的游戏测试将为错误修复和技术故障排除提供宝贵的数据。发现错误？访问 bugs.mojang.com 进行报告！其他问题？查看我们的常见问题解答。

source_string: With the full Minecraft experience, you get Creative mode, achievements, and more, plus with a Microsoft account you can meet others in the Minecraft community! You’ll be able to join friends’ worlds, make new friends on Servers, and sync your Marketplace purchases to everywhere you play Minecraft.
translation: 您可以借助完整的 Minecraft 体验获得创造模式、成就等等，另外您还可以借助 Microsoft 账号在 Minecraft 社区中结识其他玩家！您将能够加入好友的世界，在服务器上结识新的好友，并将您的市场购买内容同步到您玩 Minecraft 的任何地方。

source_string: In addition to the full Minecraft experience with Creative mode, Multiplayer, and more, you'll earn achievements and a Gamerscore to mark your Minecraft progress and show your Microsoft account friends your accomplishments.
translation: 除了获得带有创造模式、多人游戏等等的完整 Minecraft 体验，您还将获得成就和玩家分数。它们将记录您的 Minecraft 进度，并向您的 Microsoft 账号好友展示您的成就。

source_string: The full Minecraft experience lets you enjoy Creative mode, achievements and Multiplayer with your friends across Minecraft devices! Play with friends on console, PC and mobile to create, explore and survive together.
translation: 完整的 Minecraft 游戏体验能够让您享受创造模式、成就以及与您的好友在多种 Minecraft 设备上进行多人游戏！与控制台、电脑和移动端上的好友一起创造、探索和生存。

source_string: As a part of the full Minecraft experience, Servers offer some of the most creative ways to enjoy Minecraft! Play great mini-games, meet the Minecraft community and make new friends.
translation: 作为完整的《我的世界》游戏体验的一部分，服务器提供了一些享受《我的世界》的最有创意的方式！玩精彩的小游戏，邂逅《我的世界》社区并结识新的好友。

source_string: The full game allows access to Minecraft Marketplace, our in-game store. Switch up your look with new skins, change your world, or explore incredible new maps from the best community creators!
translation: 解锁完整游戏可以获得访问我们游戏内商店——《我的世界》市场的权限。用新的皮肤让自己焕然一新，更改您的世界，或者探索来自最佳的社区创建者的超赞新地图！

source_string: A beloved part of the full Minecraft experience: Creative mode! Access the entire inventory - the only limit to what you can build is your imagination! Fly around your world, make your dream home out of anything and everything, or just blow up a mountain with unlimited TNT!
translation: 完整的《我的世界》游戏体验中最受欢迎的部分：创造模式！访问整个物品栏——您能建造什么只取决于您的想象力！飞遍您的世界，用任何东西、一切东西建造您的梦想之家，或者干脆用无限量的 TNT 炸掉一座山！

source_string: Want to make wolves act like bunnies? Turn all the trees into cotton candy? You can alter everything in the full Minecraft experience with add-ons! Plus get access to Multiplayer, Creative mode, achievements and more!
translation: 想让狼表现得像兔子一样吗？把所有的树都变成棉花糖？您可以在完整的 Minecraft 游戏体验中使用附加件改变一切！此外，您还可以访问多人游戏、创造模式、成就等等！

source_string: The full Minecraft experience unlocks access to Seeds! Seeds help you discover new biomes - survive on ice plains, ascend extreme hills, or trek across deserts. Start with unique templates or explore random new worlds!
translation: 解锁完整的《我的世界》游戏体验可以获得访问种子的权限！种子会帮助您发现新的生物群系——在冰原上生存，攀登险峻的峭壁，或者徒步穿越沙漠。立即以独特的模板开始游戏或探索随机的新世界！

source_string: Get Minecraft, 700 Minecoins, 2 skin packs, 1 texture pack and 1 mash-up
translation: 获得《我的世界》、700 个 Minecoin、2 个皮肤包、1 个材质包和 1 个混搭包。

source_string: Get Minecraft, 1000 Minecoins, 4 skin packs, 2 texture packs, 3 maps, and 1 mash-up
translation: 获得《我的世界》、1000 个 Minecoin、4 个皮肤包、2 个材质包、3 张地图和 1 个混搭包。

source_string: Buy skins, textures and worlds in the Marketplace!
translation: 在市场购买皮肤、材质和世界！

source_string: Buy skins, textures and worlds in the Marketplace!
translation: 在市场购买皮肤、材质和世界！

source_string: Go on safari in a rugged off-road vehicle that seats 4!
translation: 乘坐一辆 4 座的越野车进行游览！

source_string: Explore Noxcrew's magical world full of ancient castles!
translation: 探索 Noxcrew 充满了古老城堡的奇妙世界！

source_string: Transform your Minecraft world into a comic!
translation: 将您的《我的世界》的世界转变成一部漫画！

source_string: Vast tropical wilderness on a whirlwind hunt for treasure!
translation: 广阔的热带荒野上旋风般的寻宝之旅！

source_string: Explore an ancient world, texture pack and skins!
translation: 探索古老的世界、材质包和皮肤！

source_string: Playgrounds filled with games and challenges!
translation: 充满了游戏和挑战的游乐场！

source_string: Get ready for an explosion of rainbow pastel happiness!
translation: 准备好迎接彩虹般的彩色粉笔带来的巨大欢乐！

source_string: Make your worlds simple, colorful and vibrant!
translation: 让您的世界变得简洁、多彩、生机勃勃！

source_string: Customize your character with this selection of skins!
translation: 快用这个皮肤包装扮您的角色吧！

source_string: Dress as a Cake Maniac, Frankencrafter, or Worse!
translation: 快来穿成蛋糕疯子、科学怪人或更糟糕的造型吧！

source_string: The original Minecraft experience: collect resources to craft tools and build structures, find and farm food to manage your hunger, battle dangerous mobs, and explore a vast world.
translation: 《我的世界》原始体验：收集资源来制作工具和建造结构、寻找和种植食物来填饱肚子、和危险的生物战斗，并探索广阔的世界。

source_string: Start by collecting some wood and dirt for a makeshift home to help you survive the first night! From there it's all up to you.
translation: 首先要收集一些木头和泥土来建造临时房屋，以帮助您度过第一个夜晚！之后就全看您自己了。

source_string: Build anything you can imagine in Creative Mode. Take no damage, fly through the skies, and enjoy instant access to every block in the game! This mode lets you focus on crafting and gives you everything you need to build something beautiful!
translation: 在创造模式中建造您想象得到的任何事物！不会受到伤害、在天空中翱翔、享受可立即取得游戏中所有方块的快感！这个模式让你可以专注于建造，并给予您用来建造美丽事物的全部所需。

source_string: You'll also have access to Inspiration Island, a tutorial world and introduction to Creative mode that'll teach you how to be a master builder in no time! You can find more great worlds like this in Minecraft Marketplace.
translation: 您也可以拜访灵感岛——一个世界教程和创造模式介绍，并即刻从中学习如何成为建造大师！您可以在《我的世界》市场中找到更多类似的有趣世界。

source_string: We're having trouble verifying that you own Minecraft on this device. Make sure you have downloaded and installed Minecraft from the store. Or simply reconnect to the internet and try again.
translation: 我们在确认您在这个设备上拥有《我的世界》时遇到了困难。请确保您已经从商店下载并安装了《我的世界》。或者直接重新连接到互联网并再试一次。

source_string: When you see this icon, we are saving your game. Do not turn off your device while this icon is on screen.
translation: 当您看到此图标时，我们正在保存您的游戏。当屏幕上出现此图标时，请不要关闭您的设备。

source_string: When you see this icon, we are saving your game. Do not turn off your Xbox while this icon is on screen.

source_string: Your Minecraft account lets you play online multiplayer with friends on PCs and mobile devices. And the best part?

source_string: You can use it anywhere you play Minecraft.

source_string: Favorite friends go first on your friends list. You'll see when they go online or start broadcasting.
translation: 收藏的好友会出现在好友列表的最前面。无论他们何时上线或开始直播，您都会看见他们。

source_string: Follow %s. After you both are friends, you can invite them to your game.
translation: 关注 %s。在互相关注后，您即可邀请他们加入您的游戏。

source_string: Manage your privacy settings for sharing your real name in the Xbox app.
translation: 在 Xbox 应用程序中管理用于共享您的实际姓名的隐私设置。

source_string: You've been temporarily muted in chat.
translation: 你在聊天中暂时被静音。

translation: 请记住遵循《我的世界》社区标准。

source_string: Your current skin violates our Community Standards. Please select a different skin to join a multiplayer game. Click "%s" to view our Community Standards or submit a case review for your current skin.
translation: 您当前的皮肤违反了我们的社群规则。请选择其它皮肤加入多人游戏。点击 "%s" 查看我们的社群规则或提交针对您当前皮肤的案例审核。

source_string: §eChat and other user generated text is not available on this realm right now. Please try again later.§f
translation: §e聊天文本和其他用户生成的文本目前在此 Realm 上不可用。请稍后再试。§f

source_string: Something went wrong. We can't verify that the server you are trying to connect to is one that we trust. We recommend that you try again later.
translation: 出错了。我们无法验证您尝试连接的服务器是我们信任的服务器。我们建议您稍后再试。

source_string: This is bad. This server failed our verification test. Someone we don't trust might be pretending to be a trusted server.
translation: 太糟糕了。该服务器未能通过我们的验证测试。我们不信任的服务器可能正假装成受信任服务器。

source_string: Would you like to play your world now?
translation: 您想立即开始玩您的世界吗？

source_string: Adding an external server requires knowing the server name and server IP address. Once added, the server can be found in the server list for play.
translation: 添加外部服务器需填写服务器名称和服务器 IP 地址。添加后，可在服务器列表中找到服务器进入游戏。

source_string: This server has already been added

translation: 我以为需要 Xbox 主机

source_string: Feedback: Why didn't you sign in?
translation: 反馈：您为什么没有注册？

source_string: You can hold down Shift to take a close up picture using the Camera.
translation: 您可以在按住 Shift 的同时用摄像机拍摄近景图片。

source_string: Unlike Signs, you can edit Slates, Posters, and Boards over and over again.
translation: 与标志不一样，您可以反复地编辑石板、海报和黑板。

source_string: Use Ctrl+B to turn on text-to-speech capabilities for in-game chat.
translation: 使用 Ctrl+B 打开文本转语音功能，来进行游戏内聊天。

source_string: You can export your Minecraft world to share it with others.
translation: 您可以导出《我的世界》的世界与他人共享。

source_string: To have your peers connect to your world, pause your game and share your join code.
translation: 要让同伴连接到您的世界，请暂停游戏并分享您的加入代码。

source_string: Remember that to use slash commands, you need to enable cheats in your world.
translation: 请记住，要使用斜杠命令，您需要在您的世界中启用作弊。

source_string: Done with your creation? Have others tour your world as visitors to protect your work.
translation: 已完成您的创作？让别人作为访客游览您的世界以便保护您的作品。

source_string: To code in Minecraft, press "C" on your keyboard or touch the Agent icon at the top of your screen.
translation: 要在 Minecraft 中编辑代码，请按下键盘上的“C”键或触摸屏幕顶部的代理机器人图标。

source_string: Use the Library to find new game worlds to build in.
translation: 用这个库来寻找可供创建的新的游戏世界。

source_string: Looking for a specific biome? Try the Library.
translation: 正在寻找特定的生物群系？试试库吧。

source_string: In Survival Mode, players must find their own resources.
translation: 在生存模式中，玩家必须自行找到资源。

source_string: In Creative Mode, players can freely choose to build from any of the blocks in Minecraft.
translation: 在创造模式中，玩家可以自由选择《我的世界》中的任何方块来进行建造。

source_string: Your code building robot helper is called the Agent.
translation: 您的代码创建机器人助手称为代理机器人。

source_string: Redstone can be used in Minecraft to create circuits and simple machines.
translation: 在《我的世界》中，红石可以用来创建电路和简单的机器。

source_string: You can copy and paste from a text editor to a slate, poster, board, or into chat.
translation: 您可以从文本编辑器复制粘贴内容到石板、海报、公告板或聊天中。

source_string: Show hints for commonly-used keyboard and mouse controls by pressing "H" on your keyboard.
translation: 按下键盘上的“H”按钮即可显示常用键盘和鼠标控制器的提示。

source_string: You can toggle Auto Jump on or off in the Settings menu under Controls.
translation: 您可以在“控制”下的“设置”菜单中打开或关闭“自动跳跃”。

source_string: While in Creative Mode, quickly press jump twice to fly.
translation: 在创造模式下，快速按下两次“跳跃”以飞行。

source_string: Choose a Default Game Mode when creating a world to specify the type of gameplay you want.
translation: 在创建世界时选择一个“默认课程模式”来指定您想要的探索方法。

source_string: Use the command "/setworldspawn" to have new players begin playing where you are standing.
translation: 使用 ''/setworldspawn'' 命令可以让新玩家在您所站的地方开始游戏。

source_string: Choose a default player permission when creating your world to specify the permissions you want your classmates to have when they join.
translation: 在创建您的世界时，选择一个默认的玩家权限，以指定您希望您的同学在加入时拥有的权限。

source_string: Press "I" on your keyboard or touch the Immersive Reader icon to read or translate in-game text.
translation: 按下键盘上的“I”或触摸沉浸式阅读器图标来阅读或翻译游戏内文本。

source_string: To add or change an NPC in your world, first make yourself a world builder with "/wb".
translation: 要在您的世界中添加或更改一个非用户角色，首先使用“/wb”将自己设置为世界建造者。

source_string: There's a brand new build challenge every month! Find them all in the Library under Monthly Build Challenges.
translation: 每个月都有全新的建造挑战！在“每月建造挑战”下的库中查找所有内容。

source_string: Find related lessons by clicking on tags in the Library.
translation: 单击库中的标签查找相关课程。

source_string: Game moving slowly? Try turning down the render distance in Settings.
translation: 课程加载太慢？尝试在“设置”中关闭渲染距离。

source_string: Want to use Code Builder? Make sure cheats are toggled on.
translation: 想要使用代码编辑器？确保已启用无敌模式。

source_string: Press F5 to change player perspective.
translation: 按下 F5 更改用户视角。

source_string: Use "/spawnpoint" to change your spawn point. It's just like you slept in a bed!
translation: 使用“/spawnpoint”更改生成点。就像睡在床上一样！

source_string: Most monsters only come out at night. During the day you're safe... probably.
translation: 大多数的怪物都是昼伏夜出。白天你是安全的…大概吧。

source_string: Break blocks, pick up resources. Use the crafting grid to make helpful items. Now you're crafting!
translation: 打破方块，拾取资源。使用网格合成表来制作有用的物品。尽情合成吧！

source_string: You have endless lives, but your items drop to the ground when you die. Hurry back to pick them up!
translation: 虽然你可以无限次复活，但在死亡的时候你的物品会掉到地上。快回去把物品捡回来吧！

source_string: It's a good idea to build a place where you can safely spend the night.
translation: 最好搭建一处可以安全度过夜晚的地方。

source_string: Use the right tool for the job! Chopping wood with an axe is much faster than using your hands.
translation: 使用合适的工具来劳作吧！用斧头伐木的速度要比用手快多了。

source_string: Even in Minecraft you'll get hungry, so try to find something to eat before that happens.
translation: 即使是在 Minecraft 中，你也是会感到饥饿的，所以请努力在饿肚子之前找到食物。

source_string: Digging straight down or straight up might not be a great idea.
translation: 不建议垂直往下方或上方挖掘。

source_string: Monsters spawn in the dark. Craft a torch to brighten up any space.
translation: 黑暗中会生成怪物。合成火把来照亮四周吧。

source_string: Beds are great! Craft one to quickly pass the night and set your respawn point.
translation: 床是个好东西！制作一张床，然后睡上一觉，不仅可以快速度过夜晚，还可以设置重生点。

source_string: Be careful when you swim. Stay under water for too long and you'll run out of air.
translation: 游泳时要多加小心。在水下停留太久会耗尽氧气。

source_string: Survival mode has 4 different difficulty levels - Peaceful, Easy, Normal, and Hard. Or play Creative mode and get endless resources!
translation: 生存模式有 4 个不同的难度级别：和平、简单、一般和困难。也可以玩创造模式，有无限的资源可供使用！

source_string: The world of Minecraft is endlessly surprising. You'll find lots of different animals, plants, and even §f§k§a§b§r §f§k§a§b§r
translation: Minecraft 的世界中藏有数不清的惊喜。你可以发现各种不同的动物、植物，甚至还有§f§k§a§b§r §f§k§a§b§r
context: please leave "§f§k§a§b§r" unchanged

source_string: Iron golems will fight for you!
Feed a bone to a wolf to tame it. You can then make it sit or follow you.
translation: 给狼喂骨头可以将其驯服。然后，你可以命令它坐下或跟随你。

source_string: Wearing a pumpkin on your head will keep Endermen from attacking you.
translation: 把南瓜戴在头上就不会受到末影人的攻击。

source_string: Harvest leather from cows, and use it to make armor and books.
translation: 牛身上可以收获皮革，皮革可以用来制作盔甲与书。

source_string: You can fill an empty bucket with water, lava, milk, powdered snow... and even some mobs.
translation: 空桶里可以装水、熔岩、牛奶、粉雪…甚至还能装某些生物。

source_string: Feeding an animal will keep it from despawning. Build a pen to keep your animals safe.
translation: 喂养动物可以防止其消失。建造围栏来保护你的动物吧。

source_string: Get to your destination faster with a minecart and some rails!
translation: 乘坐铁轨上的矿车，更快到达目的地！

source_string: Building a portal will allow you to travel to another dimension called the Nether.
translation: 制作传送门，通过传送门穿越到下界。

source_string: Bonemeal (crafted from a skeleton bone) can be used as a fertilizer and can make things grow instantly!
translation: 用骷髅架制作的骨粉可以用作肥料，让作物瞬间生长！

source_string: Obsidian is created when water hits a lava source block.
translation: 水与熔岩源方块碰撞时将产生黑曜石。

source_string: If the source block for water or lava is removed, it will stop the flow completely.
translation: 移除水或熔岩的源方块后，水或熔岩将彻底停止流动。

source_string: Blocks that can be used as a light source will melt snow and ice.
translation: 可用作光源的方块会使雪与冰融化。

source_string: Take caution when building structures made of wool out in the open, as lightning from thunderstorms can set wool on fire.
translation: 在户外用羊毛打造建筑时要格外小心，雷暴产生的闪电可以引燃羊毛。

source_string: A single bucket of lava can be used in a furnace to smelt 100 blocks.
translation: 一桶熔岩可供熔炉熔化 100 个方块。

source_string: The instrument played by a note block depends on the material beneath it.
translation: 音符盒奏出的乐器取决于其下方放置的材料。

source_string: Attacking a wolf will cause any wolves nearby to turn hostile and attack you.
translation: 攻击狼会导致附近的所有狼变为敌对状态并向你发起攻击。

source_string: Wolves and iron golems won't attack creepers.
translation: 狼和铁傀儡不会攻击苦力怕。

source_string: Chickens lay an egg every 5 to 10 minutes.
translation: 鸡每隔 5 到 10 分钟就会下一个蛋。

source_string: Obsidian can be mined with a diamond pickaxe.
translation: 黑曜石可以用钻石镐开采。

source_string: Creepers are the easiest obtainable source of gunpowder.
translation: 苦力怕是最容易获取的火药来源。

source_string: Tame wolves show their health with the position of their tail. Feed them meat to heal them.
translation: 驯服狼时会在它们的尾部显示其生命值。喂它们吃肉可以对其进行治疗。

source_string: Different colored dyes can be made from a variety of materials, cook cactus in a furnace to get green dye!
translation: 不同的材料可以制成不同颜色的染料，将仙人掌放进熔炉中炙烤可获得绿色染料！

source_string: Pigs that are struck by lightning become zombified piglins.
translation: 被闪电击中的猪会变成僵尸猪灵。

source_string: Sometimes iron golems give flowers to the villager children!
translation: 铁傀儡有时候会把鲜花送给小村民！
豹猫会让苦力怕知道谁才是老大！

source_string: Use seagrass to attract and breed sea turtles.
translation: 用海草来吸引和喂养海龟。

source_string: Protect baby turtles from hostile mobs!
translation: 保护小海龟免受有敌意生物的伤害！

source_string: Baby turtles will drop scutes when they grow - these can be crafted into turtle shells.
translation: 小海龟在生长时会掉落鳞甲——这些鳞甲可以用来合成海龟壳。

source_string: Brew some water breathing potions for underwater exploration!
translation: 为水下探险酿造一些水下呼吸药水！

source_string: Dolphins can lead you to shipwrecks and underwater ruins, feed them cod and follow their trail!
translation: 海豚可以将您领向沉船和水下废墟，喂它们鳕鱼并跟随它们的踪迹！

source_string: Use shears to carve a pumpkin.
There are 3587 types of tropical fish!
Sea pickles can be smelted into lime green dye.
translation: 海泡菜可被熔炼成浅黄绿色染料。

source_string: Use hay bales to breed Llamas!
Compasses always point to the world spawn - craft one to find your way!
translation: 指南针永远会指向世界生成点，合成一个指南针来为你指路吧！

source_string: Trade with villagers to obtain food, tools, and even explorer maps!
translation: 与村民交易可获得食物、工具，甚至获得探险者地图！

source_string: Did you know you can hold a map in your off-hand?
translation: 您知道您可以随手拿着地图吗？

source_string: Leads can be used on boats.
Sneak to walk safely on magma blocks.
translation: 潜行可以在岩浆块上安全地行走。

source_string: You can gather cobwebs using shears.
translation: 你可以用剪刀收集蜘蛛网。

source_string: Tridents are dropped by the Drowned, and can be held or thrown.
translation: 三叉戟由溺尸掉落，可以被握住或投掷。

source_string: You can smelt 20 items in a furnace by using a block of dried kelp as fuel.
translation: 您可以用一个干海带块作为燃料，在熔炉里冶炼 20 个物品。

source_string: Taming a skeleton horse doesn't require a saddle.
translation: 驯服骷髅马时无需马鞍。

source_string: Phantoms are dangerous mobs that appear during the night. Make sure to sleep regularly!
translation: 幻翼是会在夜间出现的危险生物。您得确保自己有规律的睡眠！

source_string: Zombies turn into drowned if they sink underwater.
translation: 僵尸沉入水下后会变成溺尸。

source_string: When digging straight up, place a torch at your feet to break any sand or gravel that could potentially fall down on you.
translation: 当您直接向上挖的时候，在您的脚边放一个火把，打破任何可能掉到您身上的沙子或砂砾。

source_string: Shear a Beehive or nest to get Honeycomb, use a Bottle to get honey.
translation: 修剪蜂箱或蜂巢以获得蜜脾，并使用瓶子获取蜂蜜

source_string: Place a campfire under a beehive or nest to harvest honey.
translation: 将营火放置在蜂窝或蜂巢下可收获蜂蜜。

source_string: Emerald ores are the rarest ores in Minecraft! They can only be found in mountains and meadows.
translation: 绿宝石矿石是 Minecraft 中最稀有的矿石！它们只会出现在山脉和草地中。

source_string: Need diamonds? They get more common as you go deeper.
translation: 需要钻石？越往深处走，这东西就变得越常见。

source_string: Frogs eat small and blocky mobs.
translation: 青蛙吃小型方块状的生物。

source_string: The Allay loves to collect items! If you give it a certain item it will try to collect more of it.
translation: 悦灵喜欢收集物品！如果给它一个特定的物品，它会试图收集更多的物品。

source_string: Frogs pick a variant based on the temperature of the biome the tadpole grow up in.
translation: 青蛙根据蝌蚪生长的生物群系的温度选择一种变体。

source_string: You can collect tadpoles in buckets.
translation: 你可以在桶中收集蝌蚪。

source_string: Ancient cities can be found under mountain ranges.
translation: 古城可以在山脉之下找到。

source_string: Allays love music and therefore interact with noteblocks!
translation: 悦灵热爱音乐，因此会与音符盒互动！

source_string: Use a water bottle on a dirt block to get mud!
translation: 在泥土方块上使用水瓶来获得泥浆！

source_string: When wandering in the deep dark, silence is key.
translation: 在漆黑中徘徊时，沉默是关键。

source_string: Some animals will follow you if you have wheat in your hand.
translation: 拿着小麦，有些动物就会跟着你。

source_string: Before you mine diamonds, redstone, or gold, make sure you're using an iron or diamond pickaxe or it won't work.
translation: 一定要用铁镐或钻石镐开采钻石、红石、黄金，否则只会徒劳无功。

source_string: Placing two chests side by side will make one large chest.
translation: 两个宝箱并排放在一起，即可获得一个大宝箱。

source_string: Can't find any coal for your torches? Try putting some logs in a furnace.
translation: 找不到火把要用的煤炭？试试把原木放进熔炉里。
无限的奇迹，无尽的可能。

source_string: Plant some saplings and they'll grow into trees.
translation: 种些树苗，待它们长成树木。

source_string: Use a hoe to prepare areas of ground for planting.
translation: 用锄头整地，为耕种做好准备。

source_string: Zombified piglins won't attack you - unless you make them angry.
translation: 僵尸猪灵不会攻击你，除非你激怒了它们。

source_string: Hit those fireballs back at the Ghast!
translation: 将那些火球打回恶魂那里！

source_string: Cobblestone is resistant to Ghast fireballs, making it useful for guarding portals.
translation: 圆石可以抵御恶魂发射的火球，可用于守卫传送门。

source_string: Our music is by C418, Lena Raine, Aaron Cherof, and Kumi Tanioka.
translation: 我们的音乐是由 C418、Lena Raine、Aaron Cherof 和 Kumi Tanioka 出品。

source_string: There will be an update to this game eventually!
translation: 最终会对此游戏进行更新！

source_string: Creepers were born from a coding bug.
translation: 苦力怕诞生于编程失误。

source_string: The first version of Minecraft was created in just 6 days!
translation: Minecraft 的第一个版本只花了 6 天时间就搭建好了！

source_string: The Enderman language is actually English in reverse.
translation: 末影人的语言实际上就是反着说的英语。

source_string: The original name for Minecraft was Cave Game.
translation: Minecraft 的原名为 Cave Game。

source_string: A Spider Jockey is the rare appearance of a spider being ridden by a skeleton!
translation: 蜘蛛骑手非常罕见，是一种骷髅骑着蜘蛛的生物！

source_string: Traveling one block in the Nether is equal to traveling eight blocks in the Overworld.
translation: 在下界中行进一个方块相当于在主世界中行进八个方块。

source_string: Use phantom membranes to repair your elytra.
translation: 使用幻翼膜来修理您的鞘翅。

source_string: Elytra can be used to glide, find them in End city ships!
translation: 鞘翅可以用来滑翔，它们会出现在末地城的船中！

source_string: Test out some new features by turning on Experimental Gameplay in the settings menu!
translation: 打开设置菜单中的实验性游戏内容，即可测试一些新功能！

source_string: Monsters that are killed by skeletons arrows have a chance of dropping music discs.
translation: 被骷髅箭消灭的怪物有机会掉落音乐唱片。

source_string: Texture packs change the way that blocks, items, and even the menus look in game. Try them out!
translation: 材质包会改变游戏中方块、物品甚至菜单的外观。试试吧！

source_string: Using firework rockets boosts elytra speed in mid air. Just... make sure they don't explode, otherwise it'll hurt BADLY!
translation: 使用焰火火箭会提高鞘翅在半空中的速度。只要…确保它们别爆炸就好，否则会让你疼得够呛！

source_string: Riptide enchantment will propel you through the air in the rain.
translation: 激流附魔将在雨中推动您穿过空气。

source_string: The Beacon is a powerful item that can only be crafted with a Nether star from the Wither!
translation: 信标是一种强力物品，只能用一颗产自凋灵的下界之星来合成！

source_string: Nether stars can't be destroyed by explosions.
translation: 下界之星不会被爆炸摧毁。
你可以与猪灵交换物品。

source_string: Respawning in the Nether requires a charged respawn anchor.
translation: 在下界重生需要充能的重生锚。

source_string: You can charge a respawn anchor with glowstone.
translation: 你可以用荧石为重生锚充能。

source_string: You can breed hoglins with crimson fungus, but be careful.
translation: 你可以用绯红真菌来饲养疣猪兽，但千万要小心。

source_string: Gold is most common in the Nether and in the badlands biome.
translation: 黄金是下界和荒地生物群系里最常见的资源。

source_string: Diorite, you either love it or hate it.
translation: 闪长岩是一种会让您对它非爱即恨的东西。

source_string: Take a screenshot using the Game menu.
A Realm is always online, so you and your friends can play here whenever you want.
translation: 有一个 Realm 始终在线，所以您和您的好友可以随时在这里游玩。

source_string: Keep up to date with what's going on in your Realm by checking the Story Feed in Realms Stories.
translation: 在 Realms 故事中查看故事动态，及时了解您的 Realm 中发生的事情。

source_string: Share your great moments with the other players on this Realm by adding a story to the Story Feed.
translation: 在故事动态中添加故事，与该 Realm 的其他玩家分享您的精彩时刻。

source_string: Check the Timeline in Realms Stories to find out when others are playing.
translation: 查看 Realms 故事中的时间线，了解其他玩家在何时进行游戏。

source_string: Access Realms Stories from the game menu while playing on the Realm.
translation: 在 Realm 上游玩时，从游戏菜单访问 Realms 故事。

source_string: Get to know your Realm's community on the Members tab in Realms Stories.
translation: 在 Realms 故事中的成员选项卡中了解您的 Realm 社区。

source_string: Use Realms Stories to get social, keep up with your friends' progress, and organize playtime.
translation: 使用 Realms 故事进行社交活动，了解好友进度，并安排游戏时间。

source_string: Bored of gravity? Jump twice to fly!
translation: 厌倦了受重力影响？那就跳跃两次开始飞行吧！
context: A fun way to tell players that they can fly if they press the jump button twice.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Summon mobs in an instant with spawn eggs.
translation: 用生成蛋立刻生成生物。
context: Players can use an item called Sawn Egg to summon animals and monsters.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Collect goat horns and fill the world with music.
translation: 收集山羊角，让世界充满音乐。
context: Goat horn is an object players can use to play loud sounds.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Combine flint and steel with a TNT block for explosive results.
translation: 将燧石与 TNT 方块相结合，产生爆炸效果。
context: Flint and steel is a tool used to create fire or to ignite certain blocks, structures and mobs. TNT will explode when you light it.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Try blinking around the map with an ender pearl. Don't get dizzy!
translation: 试试用末影珍珠在地图上闪现移动。可别头晕了！
context: An ender pearl is an item that can be thrown and teleports the thrower to where it lands.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Use rails and a minecart to build the perfect transport system. Or rollercoaster!
translation: 使用铁轨与矿车来打造完美的运输系统。造过山车也不在话下！
context: To  encourage players to build railroads{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Seeking a little more danger? Survival mode has plenty.
translation: 想多体验危险的感觉？那就玩生存模式吧，危机感绝对管够。
context: In the Game mode Survival mode you can die. In Creative you can’t.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Crossbows need ammo. Add some arrows to your inventory before going hunting.
translation: 弩需要箭矢才能使用。在出发狩猎前先往物品栏里多放几支箭吧。
context: Crossbows need ammo. Add some arrows to your inventory before going hunting.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: You can't die, but villagers can. Use that information... wisely.
translation: 你不能死，但村民可以。利用好这条信息吧…谨慎一点。
context: This means you can do things that will get villagers killed. Like attracting monsters to the village.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Villagers are great at building villages. Think you can do better?
translation: 村民们很擅长建造村庄。你觉得自己能胜过他们吗？
context: This is a prompt to encourage players to build things.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Wolves will attack skeletons to chew on their tasty bones.
translation: 狼会攻击骷髅，啃食它们美味的骨头。
context: Wolves will attack skeletons. It’s also a discrete hint that you should feel wolves with bones to tame them.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Tame wild horses by sitting on them until they're calm, then saddle up and ride off. (Note: Horses do not work like that outside of Minecraft.)
translation: 想要驯服野马，就得坐到它们身上撑到它们冷静下来为止，然后就可以装上马鞍把马骑走了。（注意：在现实生活中和在 Minecraft 世界可不一样。）
context: It’s a bit unintuitive how you tame horses. Most other animals are tamed by feeding them. Not Horses. {MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Eat as much as you want, you'll never get full! And you'll never starve.
translation: 尽情享用食物吧，你怎么吃都不会饱的！而且也不会饿死。
context: In Creative Mode you don’t get hungry. Eating the food it just for fun.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Move through solid objects using spectator mode.
translation: 使用旁观模式可穿越固体对象。
context: There is a Game mode called Spectator Mode. It allows you to fly through walls and blocks and everything.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Who needs tools? Punch your way to success and remove blocks instantly in creative mode.
translation: 有必要使用工具吗？在创造模式可立即移除方块，打通成功之路。
context: Block breaking happens very fast when you’re in Creative Mode.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Like what you see? Use the pick block button to start building with whatever you're looking at. Yes, even mobs!
translation: 喜欢你看到的内容吗？无论你看到的是什么，只要使用选择方块按钮即可开始建造。没错，生物也可以这么干！
context: There is a feature called “Pick block” that enables players to instantly equip any block they click on. If you click on a mob(animal or monster) you will get a spawn egg that summons another monster/animal of that kind.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Get there now with the /tp command.
translation: 使用 /tp 命令立刻抵达该处。
context: You can teleport yourself in Creative. You use the /tp command in the chat.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Mobs won't notice you in creative mode, but they'll still notice each other…
translation: 当你处于创造模式时，生物不会注意到你的存在，不过它们还是会注意到彼此…
context: Mobs(animals & monsters) won’t notice you in creative mode, but they’ll still notice each other… meaning that they can still kill each other.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: A warden a day keeps the… well, everything away.
translation: 一天一循声守卫…唔，万物远走高飞。
context: The Warden is a scary monster that live in underground cities.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Why not build an underwater base? It's not like you can drown.
translation: 为什么不建造一个水下基地呢？你又不会淹死。
context: You can’t drown in creative mode. So it’s possible to build underwater without danger.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Whatever you can dream, you can build. There's no limit to your resources (in creative mode...).
translation: 只有想不到，没有建不了。你的资源是无限的。（当然，是在建造模式里…）。
context: Players have endless resources in Creative mode. They get all the building blocks from their inventory.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Phantoms can't hurt you, but you can still shoo them off by using a bed. Just...not literally. You sleep in it.
translation: 虽然幻翼伤不了你，不过你还是可以用床来赶走它们。只需要躺在床上就行了。
context: Phantoms are flying mobs(monsters) that spawn when you havn't slept for a few days. They won't hurt you in Creative Mode. To get rid of them you sleep in a bed.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Have you tried swimming in lava? It's like sinking into a warm bath. Just don't try it in survival mode...
translation: 你试过在熔岩里游泳吗？跟泡温泉的感觉差不多。不过你可别在生存模式里这么干…
context: Lava doesn't hurt you in creative mode.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: A second player can't join right now.
translation: 第二位玩家当前无法加入。

source_string: You have too many controllers connected while in Local Network Mode to join this game.
translation: 您要加入的游戏在本地网络模式已连接太多控制器。

source_string: Some worlds are not available because they could not be moved. Restart Minecraft to try again.
translation: 有些世界无法访问，因为它们无法移动。请重启《我的世界》，然后重试。

source_string: Read the FAQ for more info.
translation: 阅读常见问题解答以了解更多信息。

source_string: You don't have enough free space to move your files to a new location.
translation: 您没有足够的自由空间将文件移动到新位置。

source_string: We need to move your files to a different location on your device.
translation: 我们需要将您的文件移动到设备上的不同位置。

source_string: We're in the middle of moving your data to a new location on your device. Please press resume to finish the move.
translation: 我们正在将您的数据移动到设备上的新位置。请按继续以完成移动。

source_string: We're in the middle of moving your data to a new location on your device, but you don't have enough free space.
translation: 我们正在将您的数据移动到设备上的新位置，但您没有足够的自由空间。

source_string: Please free up at least %s to continue.
translation: 请释放至少 %s 以继续。

source_string: Your files have been moved successfully. Please restart Minecraft.
translation: 您的文件已成功移动。请重新启动《我的世界》。

source_string: We couldn't move all your files. We encountered the following error: (%s).
translation: 我们无法移动您的所有文件。我们遇到了以下错误：(%s)。
正在从源文件夹收集文件...
失败（错误的目的地文件夹）
文件（文件 I/O 错误）

source_string: Failed (file I/O error or no space left)
translation: 文件（文件 I/O 错误或没有空间）

source_string: Select "Delete Now" to delete all previous log files.
translation: 选择“立即删除”以删除所有之前的日志文件。

source_string: Note: The log file for your currently active session will remain.
translation: 注意：您当前活动会话的日志文件将保留。
村庄和劫掠者村庄更新 (%s)

source_string: Based on your recent support ticket, Mojang Player Support has granted permission to upload your world. You can upload your affected world from the World Select screen or under World Settings.
translation: 根据您最近的支持凭证，Mojang 玩家支持已经批准您上传自己的世界。您可以在世界选择屏幕或世界设置下上传受影响的世界。

source_string: Do not show this screen again
